101-88a @#/ /sangs rgyas rin chen gtsug tor can la phyag 'tshal lo/ /na mo rat+na shi khi ne/ ta thA ga tA ya/ ar+ha te saM myak+saM bud d+hA ya/ tad+ya thA/ rat+ne rat+ne rat+na shi khi ne swA hA/ 'chi ba'i tshe dran na ngan song kun las rnam par grol bar 'gyur/ 'chi 'phos nas kyang sum cu rtsa gsum gnam gyi lhar skye'o/ /sangs rgyas rin chen gtsug tor gyi mtshan rjes su dran pa rdzogs so//
